## Task: Finalize Marketing Sub-Page

**Current Page** : http://localhost:3000/industries/manufacturing
**Parent Section** : [e.g., /careers, /solutions, /academy, /industries]

---

### Reference Implementation
Study these files first:
- `src/components/marketing/JoinOurTeamPage.tsx` - Compact hero pattern for sub-pages
- `src/components/marketing/CareersHub.tsx` - Parent page with scroll-flip (for context)
- `src/app/globals.css` - Utilities & animations
- `tailwind.config.ts` - Full color palette

---

### Requirements

#### 1. Compact Hero (NOT Full-Screen)
Sub-pages should NOT use the scroll-flip effect. Use a compact hero instead:

**Key patterns in JoinOurTeamPage.tsx:**
- Height: `min-h-[50vh]` with `py-20 lg:py-28`
- NO scroll listener, NO transform animations
- Breadcrumb navigation showing page hierarchy
- Same dark background treatment with organic gradients

```jsx
<section className="relative min-h-[50vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden py-20 lg:py-28">
```

#### 2. Color Strategy (IMPORTANT - Inherit from Parent)

**Brand Foundation (consistent across all pages):**
- Dark backgrounds: `charcoal-900` / `#0B1A14`
- Primary green: `forest-500/600/700`
- Accent gold: `gold-400/500/600`
- Light backgrounds: `ivory`, `cream`, `white`

**Sub-pages inherit accent from parent:**

| Parent Page | Sub-Pages | Accent Color |
|-------------|-----------|--------------|
| /careers | /careers/* | Emerald |
| /academy | /academy/* | Gold + Amber |
| /solutions | /solutions/* | Forest green |
| /solutions/cross-border | - | Purple tints |
| /industries | /industries/* | Slate/Blue |
| /contact | - | Warm gold |
| /about | /about/* | Forest + Gold |

**Accent application:**
- Hero gradient tints
- Section headline accent words
- Icon colors and backgrounds
- CTA button colors
- Card accent bars
- Badge/tag colors

---

#### 3. Design Patterns

**Breadcrumb Navigation:**
```jsx
<div className="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
  <Link href="/parent" className="text-charcoal-500 hover:text-[accent]-400 text-sm">
    Parent
  </Link>
  <ChevronRight size={14} className="text-charcoal-600" />
  <span className="text-[accent]-400 text-sm font-medium">Current Page</span>
</div>
```

**Section Headers:**
```jsx
<div className="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
  <div className="w-12 h-px bg-gold-500" />
  <span className="text-gold-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
    Section Label
  </span>
</div>
```

**Card Accents:** Left-side colored bars (1px width, full height)
```jsx
<div className="group relative bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
  <div className="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-full bg-[accent]-500" />
  <div className="p-8 pl-10">...</div>
</div>
```

**CTAs:** Angled clip-path, NOT rounded-full
```jsx
<Link
  href="..."
  className="px-8 py-4 bg-[accent]-500 text-charcoal-900 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider"
  style={{ clipPath: 'polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 95% 100%, 0% 100%)' }}
>
```

**Backgrounds:** Organic radial gradients with irregular shapes
```jsx
style={{
  background: 'radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 30%, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.12) 0%, transparent 60%)',
}}
```

---

#### 4. STRICT NO-GO LIST

**DO NOT USE:**
- Full-screen hero (100vh) - reserve for parent/hub pages only
- Scroll-flip animations - reserve for main landing pages
- `rounded-full` on buttons - use angled clip-path
- Emojis anywhere (headings, badges, CTAs, decorations)
- Generic fonts (Inter, Roboto, Arial)
- Purple-on-white gradients
- Perfect circles as decoration
- Uniform grids (3x3, 4x4)
- Generic CTAs ("Learn More", "Click Here")

**DO USE:**
- Compact hero (50vh)
- Breadcrumb navigation
- Section headers with gold line
- Card accent bars
- Angled CTAs
- Lucide icons (not emojis)
- Organic gradient shapes
- Asymmetric layouts

---

### Deliverable
Transform the page to:
1. Match JoinOurTeamPage compact hero pattern
2. Inherit accent color from parent section
3. Apply section headers, card accents, angled CTAs
4. Feel premium, authentic, human-crafted
5. Zero emojis, zero generic patterns

